{"tid":1319173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［真相］親愛的警察朋友們，繼續蒙在鼓裏吧","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T14:00:11.000Z","uid":27038,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c60f7a07523a016c532e518efe3e5d24727a8f1a","tid":1319173,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:55:48.000Z","msg":"相信，有好多人已經睇到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">盧偉聰</span></span>嘅廢府之言啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大概講下講左乜：<br />\n都係個啲啦，咩示威者好暴力，<br />\n警方好大壓力，<br />\n咩暴徒們失控balabala⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好啦，來到呢度，大家有無睇出啲咩問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗱，來𠺫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">身為一個政府高官，<br />\n完全無諗過化解呢個困局。<br />\n只要講句：<br />\n如果特首無打算再推條例，<br />\n就應該出來講撤回，來回應市民訴求。<br />\n唔好再將警方變成市民怨恨的目標。<br />\n<br />\n咁就已經可以推返個始作俑者出來之餘而又唔使你班獅子王四圍走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但佢無咁樣做，<br />\n仲要語帶挑釁，搧風點火<br />\n<br />\n目的就係等市民同警察兩邊，<br />\n互相仇恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盧偉聰唔單止無打算處理呢件事，<br />\n而係完全無諗過你班獅子王會唔會攰</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你班No9醒下啦，有事出去受嘅係你班撕紙狗丫，領功個下唔係你班狗衝噴椒撚樣丫</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea88aa8daa4975b9f61ed5c9c79134862a2a7e6","tid":1319173,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"毒藍撕子們，埋嚟睇埋嚟揀啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86f02f3c8e6f274cd5f40d0c9c80b88134df74a2","tid":1319173,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:03:40.000Z","msg